{"tid":1703514,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日又一城，有小小嘢想講","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T10:41:42.000Z","uid":45788,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d950c826da40b506b023f20260cc5ae4c106e0f","tid":1703514,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"係現場做完哨，有d嘢想講<br />\n<br />\n1.4大裝修原則冇做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，千兩冇必要裝修<br />\n<br />\n2. 又一城現場唔小手足，但當叫第一輪口號個陣冇乜回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到admin準備集人巡視業務個陣冇乜人應機<br />\n其實即係話比搞手聽勇武太小人，99%和理非，唔適合裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.係咁叫巡視，mon post狗睇完就梗係準備入嚟咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝之前起碼要有哨睇實所有出入口防狗，但今日叫咗人做冇人理<br />\n<br />\n同埋叫裝修一定係一氣呵成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係隔一陣叫裝，驚死狗準備唔切咩<br />\n<br />\n4.唔一定要裝修搞到商場收皮先叫mission complete<br />\n依家時勢，玩開個d港豬見親有示威都會自動離開<br />\n今日又一城好多都係街坊，消費個d好少，basic mission已經complete,冇必要冒太大風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，不完美，要改善<br />\n聽日準備三罷周圍suck please<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf940d7689fecad6d3c76ded5ef9903528c9533","tid":1703514,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"1111<br />\n和你塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159e0d745534e1892c0861d99a9fa15433903ac2