s=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係隔一陣叫裝，驚死狗準備唔切咩<br />\n<br />\n4.唔一定要裝修搞到商場收皮先叫mission complete<br />\n依家時勢，玩開個d港豬見親有示威都會自動離開<br />\n今日又一城好多都係街坊，消費個d好少，basic mission已經complete,冇必要冒太大風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，不完美，要改善<br />\n聽日準備三罷周圍suck please<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"個人意見 <br />\n我覺得我地係咪需要一個地下組織？<br />\n依家冇大台 所有活動需要提早宣傳 係公海討論 <br />\n敵人在暗 滲透 mon post 狗 一定好多 <br />\n我地 組織活動 敵人都會部署<br />\n對我們係大大大不利 <br />\n特別係便衣滲透 之前幾次都係黑警扮示威者 <br />\n如果我地有組織 大家都認得對方 可以提防便衣滲透<br />\n活動詳情唔會咁快傳出去 <br />\n <br />\n個人意見 大家互相討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbdc3647653094e92e48a5cecd6ff3bf110228c","tid":1703514,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c156b52d87cda782efc23e5789952685828581","tid":1703514,"uid":74775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d950c826da40b506b023f20260cc5ae4c106e0f","tid":1703514,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"係現場做完哨，有d嘢想講<br />\n<br />\n1.4大裝修原則冇做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，千兩冇必要裝修<br />\n<br />\n2. 又一城現場唔小手足，但當叫第一輪口號個陣冇乜回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到admin準備集人巡視業務個陣冇乜人應機<br />\n其實即係話比搞手聽勇武太小人，99%和理非，唔適合裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.係咁叫巡視，mon post狗睇完就梗係準備入嚟咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/